videos.title: Just How Good Is The Aetherspark, Actually?  Against the Odds
videos.description:
The Aetherspark hasn't been great in Standard, but what are the odds of winning with it in Brawl where it can be our commander so we always have access to it on turn four? Let's find out!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the gathering cards (and helps support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
